    ⍝ The (shy) result r is always an empty vector in order to make _
    ⍝ ""CopyTo"" callable from a direct function.
    ⍝ If you prefer exceptions over return codes see CopyTo
      :Access Public Shared
      ⎕IO←1 ⋄ ⎕ML←3
