    ∇ {(rc more)}←Source MoveTo__ Target;∆MoveFileEx;∆MoveFile;CurrDir;SourceDrive;TargetDrive
    ⍝ Sub-function for both, MoveTo and MoveToWithRC.
      :If 0∊⍴Source
